ActCanada Customs and Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of JAMES J. HEWITT of Penticton, British Columbia, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Peter P. Dhillon, who has resigned.
